title: New: George Maple – Where You End And I Begin feat. Grande Marshall
body:
**George Maple** moves closer to producing full on dancefloor bangers on latest track, _Where You End And I Begin_, pulling in Philadelphia’s Grande Marshall for a verse.

With shows in LA and NY later this month, alongside a full run of shows during SXSW, 2015 is already shaping up pretty nicely for the Australian singer. Check it out below.
